public interface Attributable
Represents an object which may contain attributes.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    AttributeInstance getAttribute​(Attribute attribute)
    Gets the specified attribute instance from the object.

  • Method Details

    • getAttribute

      @Nullable AttributeInstance getAttribute​(@NotNull Attribute attribute)
      Gets the specified attribute instance from the object. This instance will be backed directly to the object and any changes will be visible at once.
      Parameters:
      attribute - the attribute to get
      Returns:
      the attribute instance or null if not applicable to this object
